      </association>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8475FC7D-98C7-4745-BDB4-8C28A8D5FB43" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>PO Type : Expense</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0D4462D7-40D0-4125-892E-2B5C164D6D70" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>PO Type : CL Capital</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-01083FB2-6BE3-486D-B291-41D6F151242B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>PO Type : CT Capital</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B1EF6A3E-EA70-42B0-988C-8DDE2BA24C03" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>PO Type :  CE Expense</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7CDAE52C-FE7A-4806-872F-46A41680A8E8" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>POs will be created in the Ariba Tool for which Accrual object will be created as per entry conditions</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-25832ABE-DA92-4593-BB7B-1F03066F20D3" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Daily job run (1 times per day 3am PST)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A8831379-14A4-4151-8CDB-1885508B8B29" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Using F.80 | Reverse the Accruals</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7AA942FB-8836-4C39-88F8-8D7FB4B5353B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Postings will happen as per periods mentioned</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9E14DB12-9308-45B5-BDA2-25F938C6614E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Delegation can be created by: 
1- Admin (based on cost center or PO line item) 
2- PO Owner (based on PO)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B0CD5C71-929C-44B3-B808-DB20EB07B60F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Once - 4 days before the last working day of each period</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-74504CCF-220A-4D0B-8FD1-B9E3F0ECB272" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>No</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-ABB9B30E-EA2A-424F-A792-708D62626D65" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If the PO meets the entry condition after status in 'Resolved'</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0A08D5E2-1ECA-4542-8EE9-20FD59F470FB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If the line items which are above $100K are
1- GR checked
2- Final invoice checked
3- Line item deleted</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9BD088EF-0A5B-4A59-AE16-BB9CEBBFB881" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If the line items which are above $1M are
1- GR checked
2- Final invoice checked
3- Line item deleted</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7908CFE1-7A6D-4493-94B7-DC628666FBF8" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If the sum of line items which are above $1M are
1- GR checked
2- Final invoice checked
3- Line item deleted</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6DD45F88-66A7-41C7-84EB-EF9BD3F4B900" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If the sum of line items which are above $100K are
1- GR checked
2- Final invoice checked
3- Line item deleted</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6D74316E-DC9E-4B43-BBDE-08CAD0E575D1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>No</text>
      </textAnnotation>
